							"width": 218.80615234375,
							"height": 1277,
							"text": "We won't write all of them inside class, but will here: mapUser\nexecuteById\nexistsById\ngetUsers\ngetUserByID\ngetUserByUsername\ngetPasswordByID\nupdatePassword\nremovePassword\naddActiveSession\nremoveActiveSession\ncloseCon\naddUser\naddEmployee\nupdateEmployee\nremoveEmployee\naddStudent\naddTeacher\nupdateTeacher\nremoveTeacher\naddManager\nupdateManager\nremoveManager\naddResearcher\nupdateResearcher\nremoveResearcher\nupdateStudent\nremoveStudent\nremoveUser\nassignSupervisor\naddCourse\nremoveCourse\nupdateCourseSeniourLector\nupdateCourse\naddLesson\nassignStudentToCourse\nremoveRemoveStudentFromCourse\nassignTeacherToCourse\nremoveTeacherFromCourse\naddTeacherToLesson\nremoveTeacherFromLesson\ngetAllTeachers\ngetAllManagers\ngetAllResearchers\ngetAllResearchers2\ngetTeacherById\ngetLessonByCourseID\nmapLesson\ngetAllCourses\ngetStudentsCourses\ngetCourseById\ngetLessonByID\nsetAttendance\ngetAttendancesByCourse\ngetMarksByCourseLessons\ngetStudentLessonsByCourse\ngetAllResearchProjects\nmapResearchPaper\ngetAllResearchPaper\ngetPapersByUserId\ngetResearchPaperById\naddResearchPaper\nremoveResearchPaper\ngetProjectByUserId\naddResearchProjectToDB\naddProjectMemberToDB\naddMark\ngetMarksByCourse\ngetStudentByID\ngetStudentsByCourse\ngetTeachersByCourse\nassignHeadLector\ngetStudentsByLesson\naddRequest\ngetOwnRequests\ngetReceivedRequests\naddNews\ngetNewsByAuthorId\ngetAllNews\ngetCoursesByTeacher\ngetAllEmployees"
						},
